text: The canton of Épinal-2 is an administrative division of the Vosges department, in northeastern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Épinal.Décret n° 2014-268 du 27 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département des Vosges It consists of the following communes: #Archettes #La Baffe #Deyvillers #Dignonville #Dogneville #Épinal (partly) #Jeuxey #Longchamp #Vaudéville ==References== Category:Cantons of Vosges (department)
title: Canton of Épinal-2
